'''''A Caseira e a Catarina''''' is a very popular [[Brazil]]ian play written by [[Ariano Suassuna]] that was first published in 1962.<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.releituras.com/asuassuna_menu.asp |title=''Ariano Suassuna, Obras'' |access-date=2014-07-31 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140607051157/http://www.releituras.com/asuassuna_menu.asp |archive-date=2014-06-07 |dead-url=yes |df= }}</ref><ref>[http://www.academia.org.br/abl/cgi/cgilua.exe/sys/start.htm?infoid=227&sid=305 ''Ariano Suassuna Obras - Academia Brasileira de Letras'']</ref>
==Plot== The plot has one act. It is about a woman betrayed by her husband. Angry and in sorrow, she makes a deal with the [[devil]] and asks him to take her husband and his lover to hell.<ref>[http://www.cultura.rs.gov.br/v2/2012/05/obra-de-ariano-suassuna-estreia-no-theatro-sao-pedro/ ''Obra de Ariano Suassuna estreia no Theatro São Pedro'']</ref>
