'''Cut''' in [[clothing]], [[sewing]] and [[tailor]]ing, is the style or shape of a garment as opposed to its [[Textile|fabric]] or [[trim (sewing)|trimmings]]. 

The ''cut'' of a [[coat (clothing)|coat]] refers to the way the garment hangs on the body based on the shape of the fabric pieces used to construct it, the position of the fabric's [[grain line]], and so on.

