{{Unreferenced stub|auto=yes|date=December 2009}}
'''Sasooli''' is a [[Brahui people|Brahui]] tribe in [[Iran]], [[Afghanistan]] and [[Pakistan]]. They are ethnically [[Brahui people|Brahui]]. Baloch living in [[Balochistan (Pakistan)|Balochistan]] and [[Sindh]] speak [[Brahui language|Brahui]] and [[Balochi language|Balochi]].

