{{Infobox museum | name = Symposium de sculpture sur granit de Laongo | native_name = | native_name_lang = | image = File:Symposium accueil.JPG | imagesize = 200px | caption = Symbol on gates | alt = | map_type = | map_relief = | map_size = | map_caption = | map_dot_label = | coordinates = {{coord|12.535875|-1.284473|display=inline}} | former_name = | established = {{Start date|1989|01|13}} | dissolved = | location = | type = | accreditation = | key_holdings = | collections = [[Granite]] [[Sculpture#Materials and techniques|sculpture]] | collection_size = | visitors = | founder = Siriki Ky | director = | president = | chairperson = | curator = | historian = | owner = | publictransit = no | car_park = | parking = | network = | website = none | embedded = }}
Founded in 1989, by Burkinabe sculptor Siriky Ky,<ref name=beauceky>{{cite web|url=http://www.beauceart.com/fr/siriki_ky|title=SIRIKI KY|website=http://www.beauceart.com/|publisher=Beauce Art, L'International de sculptures|accessdate=May 13, 2015|language=French}}</ref> the symposium takes place on a site located about 35&nbsp;km from [[Ouagadougou]], in the province of [[Oubritenga]]. Invited sculptors create their works ''in-situ'' using granite from the site. Some works combine local granite and other materials such as metal.
The first iteration of the biennal symposium opened January 13, 1989, gathering 18 sculptors from 13 countries.<ref name=rivages>{{cite web|title=Le site de Laongo – symposium international de sculptures de granit|url=http://rivagesdumamouausahel.over-blog.com/article-site-de-laongo-88387538.html|website=Rivages association de solidarité internationale – Burkina Faso – boucle du Mouhoun – du Mamou au Sahel de Giou à Tougan Rivages association de solidarité internationale|publisher=Rivages association de solidarité internationale – Burkina Faso – boucle du Mouhoun – du Mamou au Sahel de Giou à Tougan Rivages association de solidarité internationale|accessdate=May 13, 2015|language=French|date=July 9, 2010}}</ref>
The tenth edition took place over twenty days in May 2012.<ref>{{cite news|last1=Ouedraogo|first1=Privat|title=Burkina Faso: Symposium sculpture sur granit de Laongo – Bientôt une nouvelle dimension à l'événement|url=http://fr.allafrica.com/stories/201205220802.html|accessdate=May 13, 2015|work=Sidwaya Quotidien|date=May 21, 2012|language=French}}</ref>
As of 2010, the legal status of the site was unclear, with overlaps and gaps in jurisdictions.<ref name=memoirestatus>{{cite book|last1=Ouédraogo|first1=Zoéwendsaongo Fabrice|title=Analyse de la situation juridique du site de sculpture sur granite de Laongo|date=2011|publisher=Ecole Nationale d'Administration et de Magistrature|location=Burkina Faso|language=French}}</ref>
